text: The following lists events that happened in 1949 in Iceland. ==Incumbents== *President - Sveinn Björnsson *Prime Minister - Stefán Jóhann Stefánsson, Ólafur Thors ==Events== ==Births== Ásta Ragnheiður Jóhannesdóttir *21 January - Kristín Marja Baldursdóttir, writer *18 February - Ingibjörg Pálmadóttir, politician. *3 March - Hreinn Halldórsson, track and field athlete *9 April - Guðni Ágústsson, politician *23 June - Ragnheiður Ríkharðsdóttir, politician. *22 August - Þórarinn Eldjárn, writer *16 October - Ásta Ragnheiður Jóhannesdóttir, politician ==Deaths== ==References== Category:1940s in Iceland Iceland Iceland Category:Years of the 20th century in Iceland
